  <div style="font-weight:normal; font-size:13px;">
  <h2 style="color:#666; font-size:22px; font-weight:normal; border-bottom:1px solid #ddd;">Vik Content Slider</h2>
  <p>Module to create Image or Content Slideshows.<br/><strong>How-to:</strong><br />
   This module allow you to create a slider of differents type of content.<br />
Before to configure it you need to create the “vikcslider” folder inside the “Images” folder of Joomla and upload there the vikcslider images. <br />
After you do it, you have five fields for each image:<br />
- <strong>Background image</strong><br />
This field allow you to choose an image as background for the slide.<br />
- <strong>Image</strong><br />
This field allow you to choose an image that will appears over the background image choosed in the first field<br />
- <strong>Title slide</strong><br />
In this field you can write the title of your slide<br />
- <strong>Text</strong><br />
This is the field for the description of your slide<br />
- <strong>Read More Link</strong><br />
In this field you may to insert a link for your slide<br />

You can configure VikContentSlider, so go to Extensions > Module Manager, edit the VikContentSlider module and set up width of the slider, pay attention to write your value with the unit “px” or “%” like the default value.</p>
